The '''''Gratua''''' ([[Mando'a/Legends|Mando'a]] for "Vengeance") was a [[Kandosii-type dreadnaught|''Kandosii''-type dreadnaught]] that fought at the [[Taris Siege|Siege of Taris]].

In that conflict, [[Cassus Fett]] ordered ''[[Parjai]]'' and ''Gratua'' to return the captures to the south orbital area of [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] for processing.

